## CI
- [CI-01] **MUST** run lint, typecheck, unit tests, integration tests (containers), SAST, and dependency audit.
- [CI-02] **MUST** build reproducible, signed artifacts; generate SBOM.

## CD
- [CD-01] **SHOULD** deploy to staging on main merge; require approval/automated checks for prod.
- [CD-02] **SHOULD** use canary/blue-green when feasible; **MUST** enable automated rollback on SLO breach.

## Secrets & Config
- [CI-SEC-01] **MUST** use protected environments/secrets; **MUST NOT** echo secrets in logs.
